headline: Better Dividend Stock: Simon Property Group vs. Federal Realty Investment Trust
summary: They both have high-quality portfolios and financial profiles.  Real estate investment trusts (REITs) often make great dividend stocks.  Simon Property Group (NYSE: SPG) and Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) are two of the largest REITs focused on the retail sector.
